Johannesburg – Limpopo music and dance darling Makhadzi recently celebrated her 25th birthday in style. Makhadzi, who threw a glamorous black and gold themed affair posted her
pictures on social media. She also left the internet in shock after revealing what many thought, was an “ugly” cake for her 25th birthday. Though most social media users loved her look and decor they were not charmed by her cake dubbing it an “ANC cake” because of its black and green colours. View the cake below as well as some of the star’s birthday snaps she shared on social media along with some well-wishes from fans: <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-84690" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27-640x800.jpeg" alt="" width="640" height="800" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27-640x800.jpeg 640w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27-200x250.jpeg 200w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27-696x870.jpeg 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27-336x420.jpeg 336w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-06-at-12.56.27.jpeg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" />       Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here. Sunday World 